## Station click counter

> **Syntax:**

```json
<%= config[:api_server] %>/json/url/stationuuid
```

```xml
<%= config[:api_server] %>/xml/url/stationuuid
```

```plaintext
<%= config[:api_server] %>/m3u/url/stationuuid
```

```ini
<%= config[:api_server] %>/pls/url/stationuuid
```

> **Results:**

```json
{
    "ok": "true",
    "message": "retrieved station url",
    "stationuuid": "9617a958-0601-11e8-ae97-52543be04c81",
    "name": "Station name",
    "url": "http://this.is.an.url"
}
```

```xml
<result>
    <status 
        ok="true" 
        message="retrieved station url" 
        stationuuid="9617a958-0601-11e8-ae97-52543be04c81" 
        name="Station name" 
        url="http://this.is.an.url"
    />
</result>
```

```plaintext
#EXTM3U
#RADIOBROWSERUUID:9617a958-0601-11e8-ae97-52543be04c81
#EXTINF:1,Station name
http://this.is.an.url
```

```ini
